pd_0_com_0text: I tell you John. This is the end of the world! I swear it!
pd_1_com_0text: Ohh boohoo, Don’t be a wussie. One tower gets attacked and it’s the end of the world!
pd_3_com_0text: Have you taken the king’s shilling?
pd_5_com_0text: Ahh, then it’s not of your concern, is it?
pd_6_com_0text: Are we not going to warn the people of what happened?
pd_8_com_0text: I may not be a soldier but I can still help.
pd_8_com_1text: I probably have seen more combat than you two bozos.
pd_8_com_2text: In that case I will spend the afternoon galavanting with your mother then.
pd_9_com_0text: A dragon just attacked the tower. The two guards inside were burned alive. It was awful.
pd_10_com_0text:
Be a guard they said. No real danger they said…
Should have followed my dreams and become a painter.
pd_11_com_0text: You idiot. Ok so now you know. Don’t tell the town folk, alright?
pd_12_com_0text: No problem. So is there something I can do?
pd_13_com_0text: Well not really. Except killing the dragon of course.
pd_14_com_0text: Ok, where did he fly to?
pd_15_com_0text: Ohh... Mhmm, you are serious about it? He went inside the mountain.
pd_16_com_0text: Please kill him. I don’t want to be eaten by that thing!
pd_17_com_0text: Tsss, don’t mind him. Good luck on your journey! May God save you!
pd_19_com_0text: Is that so? So you were at the battle of Devilten town?
pd_21_com_0text: Ah so you didn’t see thousands of people burned to ashes.
pd_24_com_0text: No but I did kill a goblin just some moments earlier...
pd_25_com_0text: A goblin? What are you? A level 3 Runscape character? Pathetic...
pd_27_com_0text: Don’t mind him... He is just mad at the whole world for some reason…
pd_28_com_0text: So you are a tough guy, eh?
pd_29_com_0text: I am curious how tough when standing at the executioner’s block...
pd_34_com_0text: Pff guards... Filth of the earth. Filth I tell you...
